name: EventEntityDamaged
description: This event is fired when any entity in the world takes damage.
overview:
Fires when any entity (not just the player) takes damage.
Includes mobs, animals, item entities, etc.
The `health` field represents current health after the damage.
The `damage` field is the amount of damage taken.
Not cancellable

methods.name: toString
methods.description: Returns a string representation of the event object.
